{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act45side", "eventName": "無憂夢囈", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "SS-6", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "回聲飄蕩的大廳", "storyInfo": "祥子狼狽地回到夢城堡中，莫菲絲嘲笑祥子一次次的失敗，Ave{@nbs}Mujica沒有一個人想和她回到現實。莫菲絲表示自己為祥子準備了一個絕佳的夢境。祥子重新回到了執行羅德島外勤任務時所乘坐的車裡，本以為只是曾經的夢境再次重演，沒想到這次的夢境出現了偏差。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness02_intro", "key": "$darkness02_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "寒風在耳邊呼嘯而過。"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下墜，越來越快。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然而即便如此，深淵仍不見底。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.5, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lmstreet_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我那些強人所難的要求，除了你還有其他鼓手能滿足嗎？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是我見過的，最努力的鼓手。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你明明……只需要做你自己就好。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#13$2"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g2_srcalley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在各個組織間忙碌，卻找不到一個真正的落腳之處……這就是你想要的生活嗎？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#12$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你本來不該承受這種痛苦……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "