: "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "急促的心跳，失控的呼吸，還有背脊上的冷汗。"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "知覺再次回到了祥子體內，卻是以這種狼狽不堪的方式。"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t很真實吧？", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t從不知道多高的地方，向地面墜落。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t還有夢境破碎，被困在“無夢之境”又無法逃脫……感覺如何呢？", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "即使那些夢都是美夢，它們也不該繼續下去。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "窺竊她們心裡最脆弱的部分，再將那些脆弱不斷地編排演繹……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我並不這麼認為哦。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t在你闖進她們的夢之前，她們幾乎就快忘記你，還有那個根本無足輕重的樂隊了。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Ave{@nbs}Mujica是我們的契約，她們把人生託付給我了——", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#13$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t在乎它的只有你一個人吧！", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#13$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什麼——！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是都親耳聽見了嗎？", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她們每一個人，全都拒絕了你。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spiritwhoosh", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_lmstreet_1", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不要，這裡的人愛著身為女演員的我。", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$3"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#7$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為了這些，拼盡了一切……結果你告訴我這些都是假的？", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#7$3"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說什麼鬼話，我不可能接受！", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$4"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$4", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡是我的夢境，只有我自己就好了！", "name": "祐天寺若麥"}, "figure_art": "avg_4185_amoris_1#2$4"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spiritwhoosh", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "33_g2_srcalley", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼可能理解我？", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣的生活就很好……這樣更適合我。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#9$3"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#3$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不需要誰來拯救。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#3$3"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#3$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也沒有人能救我。", "name": "八幡海鈴"}, "figure_art": "avg_4186_tmoris_1#3$3"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spiritwhoosh", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g4_islandharbor_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sea", "volume": 0.6, "loop": "true", "channel": "sea"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "stopSound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_sea", "fadetime": 0.5, "channel": "sea"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_spiritwhoosh", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_n", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t果然，小睦根本不需要祥子。", "name": "“睦”"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "65_g2_dreamcastlehall", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈哈哈……哈哈哈哈哈哈！", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你所有狼狽、無助、可笑的時刻，我全都看在眼裡。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然之前你毀了我創造的夢境，不過這樣算下來，我們也算扯平了。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t另外還要謝謝你，在她們的夢裡一次又一次穿梭……", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t幫我證明——我創造的夢境就是完美無缺、無可挑剔的。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t現在那個傢伙也該承認，我才是夢城堡裡最有天賦的人了。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個傢伙？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#9$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你不是在夢裡見過她嗎？", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#5$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t穿著貴族小姐般華麗的衣服，嘴裡說著一些老掉牙的客套話。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t待在她的身邊，簡直讓人坐立難安。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛麗絲才是這裡的主人，你只是一個冒牌貨！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她說過，再美好的夢，最後也應該醒來——", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔——！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子只覺得自己的聲帶被凝結，無法發出任何的聲音。"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我終於知道你為什麼讓我這麼討厭了。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#15$1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你和她一樣，完全不聽別人的想法，嘴裡也永遠都是那些虛偽又空洞的說辭。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t說什麼託付了人生，其實是不想自己被人捨棄吧。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t我看過你的人生，就只是一個落魄大小姐的不甘和掙扎。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#9$1"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你的每一個舉動，無非就是在欺騙和說服自己，不想讓其他人覺得你落魄而已。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#10$1"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#10$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你這個人自負自傲、自私自利，簡直無可救藥。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#10$1"}, {"id": 214, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#16$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你的樂隊到底代表著什麼？哼，只是一群人用所謂的契約互相束縛，自娛自樂。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#16$1"}, {"id": 216, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t現在她們都得到了幸福，當然就拋棄你了。豐川祥子，你又是孤身一人了。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t既然你相信愛麗絲說的那些話，那好，我為你重新準備了一場好夢。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t這場夢天衣無縫，就算你知道它是假的，你也不會願意醒來。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你會和你的同伴們一樣，沉溺其中，無法自拔。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#1$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔——！", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$1"}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t想說話？那就讓你說最後一句。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#11$1"}, {"id": 228, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "惡魔般的少女在空中比劃了一個圖案，彷彿解開了什麼鎖鏈。"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我——", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$1"}, {"id": 233, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "鎖鏈又被狠狠地拉緊。"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t哈哈哈哈哈哈——", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#19$1"}, {"id": 238, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t果然，你還是不說話的時候比較可愛！", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 240, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "莫菲絲一步步靠近掙扎的祥子，她伸出了右手，放在了祥子的臉頰上。"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t虛偽的公主啊，在你剛才漫遊奇境時，我已經完全瞭解你了。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 243, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你最渴望什麼，你最需要什麼，你最害怕什麼。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 245, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t別擔心，這次的夢，一定是完美的美夢。你會無比清醒，卻絕對不會想甦醒。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#18$1"}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 沉眠吧。高貴的、狡猾的、自私的，人偶少女。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1"}, {"id": 249, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t祝你，有個好夢。", "name": "莫菲絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1942_1#17$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 252, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 254, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 3.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "匡噹，匡噹。"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子，祥子？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……嗯？", "name": "豐川祥子"}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "46_g1_transporter", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我不是你說的那樣——", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#4$2"}, {"id": 269, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "祥子失聲叫了出來，但她如今已不在城堡內，莫菲絲也消失得無影無蹤。"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 272, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#4$1", "focus": "m", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你還好嗎？你的臉色很難看，是不是又做惡夢了？", "name": "紅豆"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#4$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我又……回到自己的夢裡了。", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t你在說什麼傻話，你不是才剛醒過來嗎？", "name": "紅豆"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#4$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t是不是睡昏頭了？", "name": "紅豆"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#4$1"}, {"id": 282, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛麗絲和貝娜也在……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_338_iris_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你好……我好像還沒自我介紹過？", "name": "愛麗絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_338_iris_1#1$1"}, {"id": 286, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_369_bena_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們上車的時候，她好像已經睡著了？", "name": "貝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#5$1"}, {"id": 288, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我和紅豆沒有遲到……夢發生改變了……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#6$2"}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t祥子，你從剛才就一直在說一些奇怪的話——", "name": "紅豆"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#11$1"}, {"id": 292, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.6, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "我們正在前往維多利亞的一個小鎮，目的是去找一個和愛麗絲熟識的，名叫“安”的女孩。", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "Subtitle", "attributes": {"text": "而這輛車會在不久後爆胎，我們被迫停下來修補輪胎，因此延誤幾個小時……", "x": 300.0, "y": 350.0, "alignment": "center", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 700.0}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "subtitle", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們，現在要去維多利亞找安嗎？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#11$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t安是誰？愛麗絲你認識嗎？", "name": "紅豆"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#11$1"}, {"id": 305, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_338_iris_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不認識，安是祥子小姐在小鎮的朋友嗎？", "name": "愛麗絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_338_iris_1#4$1"}, {"id": 307, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸……？愛麗絲也不知道嗎？", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#14$2"}, {"id": 309, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那我和紅豆……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 311, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "\t不就是因為剛好有派到你家附近的工作嗎？我就想說讓你也順便回家休息一下，順便看望家人。", "name": "紅豆"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#1$1"}, {"id": 313, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_290_vigna_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": " 一直忙於工作，祥子你也很久沒有回家了吧。", "name": "紅豆"}, "figure_art": "avg_290_vigna_1#5$1"}, {"id": 315, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$drift", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 20.0, "ystrength": 20.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_338_iris_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼回事，車怎麼突然停下來了？！", "name": "愛麗絲"}, "figure_art": "avg_338_iris_1#4$1"}, {"id": 322, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_369_bena_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不會爆胎了吧？！", "name": "貝娜"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#5$1"}, {"id": 324, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼……呼……呼……剛才差點撞上馱獸了！", "name": "司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#5$1"}, {"id": 326, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "幸好有驚無險，我們馬上重新出發！", "name": "司機"}, "figure_art": "avg_369_bena_1#5$1"}, {"id": 327, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "豐川祥子"}, "figure_art": "avg_4182_oblvns_1#10$2"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "隨著發動機重新運作的聲音，窗外的風景再次移動了起來。"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_wilderness_d", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一模一樣的荒原，一模一樣的同行者。"}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但夢境，已然發生偏差。"}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}